Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:58.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebelling human vermin have connected \Nthe Dragon Chain Cannon to the giant lacrima
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and are trying to crash it into Extalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:06.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nichiya-sama, as well as the majority of the \NRoyal Guard, have been turned into a lacrima,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and are now being held \Ncaptive in the Royal City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Extalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How incredibly reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fearsome indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think they would go so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:23.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, one of the Fallen and \Na human have appeared in the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:26.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and are spreading the word to \Nabandon Extalia and escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:30.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're causing a riot outside of the \Ncastle... How should we deal with the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you intending to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Boy Back Then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and destroy the lacrima and \Nturn everyone back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's accelerating, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:06.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:16.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let it collide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Legy-pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! We're not coming \Neven close to stopping it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, release your magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finish this later, cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Running for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:17.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't runnin' or hidin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:20.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stop this thing and finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it? You're going to {\i1}stop{\i0} it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire floating island \Nconnected to the Dragon Chain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a fool's errand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no tomorrow for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After{\i0} this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm taking you back to my \Nguild one way or the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'm gonna make you my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, they're going to hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brace for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:18.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you returned everyone \Nelse to normal like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That black cat got in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. It'd \Ntake too much time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:34.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're totally gonna stop it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco, why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:43.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that I don't \Nneed eternal magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have eternal smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and escape, Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:52.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, you'll \Nnever stop this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if this body crumbles to bits, \NI'll stop it just with my soul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:02.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:14.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Army is attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The humans are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're planning on rebelling \Nagainst the Exceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Those damn humans don't \Nrealize our Queen's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:30.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll learn some respect today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure our Queen's magic \Nwill come out anytime now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I hope we counterattack soon, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:39.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't be afraid! Our Queen is with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lacrima hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:44.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not done yet. It seems to have \Nstopped at the edge of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to turn out like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? It's \Ntoo early to give up hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here, you Fallen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nady-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:04.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:11.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Throwing stones... is... dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a Fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:18.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These people came here to warn us of danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:21.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But because no one listened to \Nthem, it's turned out like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With our Queen's magic, something \Nlike this is no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the Queen will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Nady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is the Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please raise your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:14.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then listen calmly to what I am about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Queen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I bet she's gonna do some \Nincredibly destructive magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:25.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Extalia is on the \Nbrink of complete destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a fate we can no longer resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I have made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna wipe out all the humans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay silent and listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it, Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that I must \Ntell everyone the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am simply an Exceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:56.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am hardly a Queen, and \Nmost definitely not a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am an Exceed, the same as you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:02.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no power to fight the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I am one-winged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:16.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For an Exceed, one's wings grow and \Nshrink by one's own magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With both wings, one can display \None's true magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic power is extremely weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so sorry I hid all of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:31.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Wendy-san and Carla-san, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must apologize to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, do not hate me, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who created the \N"Queen" were we elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are a very weak race.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:58.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since long ago, we have had terrible \Nthings done to us by the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, to protect ourselves, we made \Nthe humans believe that we had power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for all Exceeds to gain \Nback their self-confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we had everyone in Extalia believe that \Nthey were protected by the power of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of God was nothing more than \Na bluff known only to us few Exceeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, the humans didn't believe us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but before long they began \Nto fear the power of God...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:37.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, the Human Control \Nthat decides when humans die...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all actually after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't decide what humans are killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have such power, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:51.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing we have is that Chagot \Ncan see a little bit into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can see people's deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:59.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When she was correct, we made people \Nthink it was she who killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Queen is God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:11.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chagot-sama, hurry and destroy the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were deceived!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:21.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not you actually have power, \Nyou ordered me to kill my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:23.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That I know to be the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chagot never gave such an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been the humans \Nwho used the Queen to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:33.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You placed strange memories, \Nmessing with my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ordered me to eliminate \Nthe Dragon Slayers, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since before I even hatched!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-N-No! There's a really long, \Nimportant reason for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there is a reason, \NI'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:50.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, now is really not the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla-san is completely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You had no sin in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:07.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I made you bear the \Nmost painful feelings of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Q-Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pass judgment on me \Nfor my sins by your own hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass judgment by your own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who love both the Exceed and \Nthe Humans, have such a right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone, get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My fate lies alongside \NExtalia as it falls to ruin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to leave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:03.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of our history...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the Queen felt she \Nhad to tell us everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:11.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to be with you, Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:17.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, you can't! This country \Nis fated for destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:32.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you just give up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your country, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:43.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do anything \Nwithout a god or queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you try your best to \Nlive on, even if it was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you giving up so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you're weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If everyone works together, \Nyou can accomplish anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This country will not be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's my homeland!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop it, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:28.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:29.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nady...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I love this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm gonna be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop this... We have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:15:01.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something humans can do anything \Nabout, no matter how strong they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:11.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give up... on \NFairy Tail... or on Extalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:14.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna protect them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:26.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna protect it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I bet everyone else does, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:37.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:01.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll protect our country ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:05.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We came through dangerous times and \Nprotected our country and its people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For our Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy-san, Carla-san... \NWe're sorry about before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we've got to do \Nsomething about this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chagot, with your wing, you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:21.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I must!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must do what I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What dream is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Extalia has joined together as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:47.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, why did you save a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the child was seriously wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:54.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Bringing that {\i1}thing{\i0} to \NExtalia is a grave offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:58.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I must help the \Ninjured, even if they be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't forget the rules, right, Lily?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are now made one of the Fallen, \Nand are banished from Extalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:08.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! For this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:28.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry... It wasn't \Nyour fault I was banished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First thing I must do is escort you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:44.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired from lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:11.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I may resent \Nit, Extalia is my country!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:13.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with this many Exceed, \Nthey can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone! This is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have stopped them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:31.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have stopped the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings... I know your \Nfeelings will get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:44.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall ne'er give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:59.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna stop it, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll push, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:27.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lacrima is being pushed back..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lacrima has disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Chain Cannon's chain as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:49.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been returned to Earthland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:58.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched for the remaining tear from the \Ngiant Anima to return everything to the way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my lateness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without everyone's help, \NI wouldn't have made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:04.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The way it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:13.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lacrima has passed once again through the \NAnima and returned to how it was in Earthland.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We protected Extalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily, you saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad I was able to \Nprotect your homeland...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:54.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Prince is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:55.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Black cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:17.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:58.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Happy, there's a dragon-looking \Nthing out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there something like that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:05.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're talking about the \NDragonoid... But this one looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.81,0:24:07.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both just fake dragons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bust it up like I did the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. If it's just coming out \Nnow, there must be something to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Dragon Sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:19.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this thing? \NMagic doesn't work on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:21.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Natsu! It's changing color!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.51,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this isn't dragon \Nslaying, it's chameleon slaying.
